net.metanotion.util.skiplist.SkipList<K,V>

All Implemented Interfaces:
Closeable, Flushable, AutoCloseable, Iterable<V>
public class BSkipList<K extends Comparable<? super K>,V> extends SkipList<K,V> implements Closeable
On-disk format: 
    Magic number (long)
    first span page (unsigned int)
    first level page (unsigned int)
    size (unsigned int)
    spans (unsigned int)
    levels (unsigned int)
Always fits on one page.
